{"tid":1790093,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"求下你地認真每日幫手Twitter國際戰線，得佢地先幫到星光，求你","createTime":"2019-12-19T17:29:18.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-20T17:59:48.000Z","uid":295459,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"6e3246cb43f8c32d4a02c4cf7ff12346486c56ee","tid":1790093,"uid":295459,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-19T17:29:18.000Z","msg":"星光係幫緊被捕手足<br />\n而家星光被警犬凍結哂d錢<br />\n唔知會令到幾多手足坐耐左<br />\n或者由唔駛坐變要坐<br />\n<br />\n而家捐錢都唔得呀<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n求下你地幫手<br />\n再進攻國際戰線<br />\n<br />\n一定要煲大件事<br />\n唔係唔只星光<br />\n仲有好多手足會糟央架<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9dde1d0702d0726f005d44cb59371ac24ac7365d","tid":1790093,"uid":30836,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-19T17:32:19.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">火</span>"},{"pid":"41aa573c98b2b7c7b32b9c0268a85ad90adb94f5","tid":1790093,"uid":27196,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-19T17:33:39.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"54caf20fe42c3affda744c7be51a024106354bb8","tid":1790093,"uid":271334,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-19T17:47:31.000Z","msg":"星火<br />\n<br />\n<br />\nSorry 借個位 捐個錢 告黑警<br />\n<br />\n許智峰 公民起訴抗警暴［大家埋黎捐$10又好，告班黑警］<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1789953\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1789953</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"4ab89a4c162ab29f4083ea979d2dc700009b2af0","tid":1790093,"uid":311583,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-19T19:09:16.000Z","msg":"<im